        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Rolagem de Ataque Corpo a Corpo: +6, alcance 5 ft. Acerto: 13 (3d6 + 3) Perfurante de dano. If o alvo is a Large or smaller creature, the cloaker attaches to it. While the cloaker is attached, o alvo has the Cego condition, and the cloaker can't make Bite attacks against other targets. In addition, the cloaker halves the de dano it takes (round down), and o alvo takes the same amount of de dano. The cloaker can detach itself by spending 5 feet of movement. The target or a creature within 5 feet of it can take an action to try to detach the cloaker, doing so by succeeding on a DC 14 Força (Athletics) check.</p>",
